description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. Totally non-scripted, all in front of a live audience, all broadcast live to members. Today's update is RD 2 of 4 of last months Live Tag Team Match up.
The top Four contenders of last season all on the mat for one amazing Tag Team Match up. The best of the best. Ariel X(1) and Darling(3) vsBella Rossi(2) and Cheynenne Jewel(4)
In round 2, the action amps up with 2 on 1 fingering-fests, brutal wrestling and fierce competition in front of the live audience!
